Share with:
Head of Telesales Job (Consumer Goods), Jakarta, Indonesia
Country:
Indonesia
Function:
Sales
Industry:
Logistics
Position type:
Permanent
Salary:
Rp. 18.000.000 - Rp. 25.000.000
Created:
02 May 2014
Monroe Consulting Group is recruiting on behalf of rapidly growing multinational consumer goods company. Our respected client is seeking a sales professional with at least five years’ experience with a respectable consumer goods company, including three years in a managerial role, for the job of Head of Telesales, to be based in Jakarta, Indonesia. This job is only open to professional salespersons who are highly motivated to increase sales.
Key job responsibilities will include:
Manages and drives performance of TeleSales team
Develops and executes TeleSales plan
Applies local sales incentive schemes for TeleSales channel based on defined sales index
Ensures achievement of country sales index for TeleSales team
Steers and improves sales performance through effective processes and performance measurement
Plans and manages portfolio of small business customers
Support TeleSales specialist in winning, retaining and developing Business Customers in SBC segment
Acts as a coach for TeleSales Team
Requirements:
Bachelor’s degree (min.)
Five years’ experience (min.) in sales in forwarding industry with 3 years at managerial level
Good understanding of the forwarding industry and deep knowledge on DGF products (AFR/OFR) and business models
Well-developed management skills and collaborative leadership style to steer sales team
Ability to take ownership and proactively address topics
Good communication, presentation and negotiation skills
Ability to win, develop and close new business
Ability to identify customer needs by gathering information and building long-term relationship
Fluent in English verbal/written communication
All applications will be treated in the strictest of confidence.